HEADWORD: Carbon steel
<hw>Carbon steel</hw>. <def>Steel deriving its qualities from carbon
chiefly, without the presence of other alloying elements; -- opposed to
<contr>alloy steel</contr>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

